<div class="container" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col border">
            <h3>Quality of Life</h3>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Training Barrels complete, start with Simian Slam, spawn in DK Isles, Japes lobby entrance open.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="fast_start_beginning_of_game" value="True" checked />
                    Fast Start - Beginning of Game
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option enables the following quality of life changes to the game:
- Removes first time text.
- Removes first time boss cutscenes.
- Removes first time area visit cutscenes.
- Removes banana dance cutscenes.
- Remove cutscenes from the startup sequence.
- Story Skip option in the main menu set to On by default.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="quality_of_life" value="True" checked />
                    Quality of Life Changes
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option will allow you to switch kongs almost anywhere using DPad left or DPad right.
You will still need to unlock the kong you want if Unlock All Kongs isn't enabled.
You cannot switch kongs in rooms or areas that would otherwise break the puzzle.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="enable_tag_anywhere" value="True" />
                    Enable Tag Anywhere
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col border">
            <h3>Unlocks</h3>

            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option will make all 5 kongs available from the start without freeing them.
The golden bananas awarded when freeing specific kongs still must be collected even with this option on.
If using Level Progression Randomizer and playing through glitchless, this option is forced on.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="unlock_all_kongs" name="unlock_all_kongs" value="True" checked disabled />
                    Unlock All Kongs
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option will make all moves available from the start without purchasing them.
Includes all Cranky, all Candy, and almost all Funky purchasables.
Does not include access to JetPac in Cranky; you will still need 15 banana medals.
Does not include snipe scope to reduce 1st person camera lag. Is still purchasable.
Does not include the shockwave attack from the banana fairy queen.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="unlock_all_moves" value="True" />
                    Unlock All Purchasable Moves
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option makes the fairy camera and shockwave attack available from the start.
Normally obtainable by visiting the Banana Fairy Queen with Tiny as Mini Monkey.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="unlock_fairy_shockwave" value="True" />
                    Unlock Fairy Camera and Shockwave Attack
                </label>
            </div>

            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="This option will shorten the time it takes to beat Hideout Helm with the following changes:
- You will spawn in the Blast o Matic room.
- Opens the roman numeral doors to each Kong's room.
- The gates in front of the music pads are gone.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="fast_start_hideout_helm" value="True" checked />
                    Fast Start - Hideout Helm
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="You do not need to collect 4 crowns to collect Key 8.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="crown_door_open" value="True" checked />
                    Open Crown Door
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="You do not need to collect the Nintendo and Rareware coin to collect Key 8.
You will not be able to collect the GB from DK Arcade with this option enabled.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="coin_door_open" value="True" checked />
                    Open Nintendo + Rareware Coin Door
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="w-100"></div>
        <div class="col border">
            <h3>Difficulty</h3>
            <div>
                Damage
                <select name="damage_amount" style="width: 60%;" class="form-select center-div" aria-label="Damage Options">
                    <option selected value="default">Normal</option>
                    <option value="ohko">OHKO</option>
                    <option value="double">Double Damage</option>
                    <option value="quad">Quad Damage</option>
                </select>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Tag Barrels, Boss Fights, Candy Upgrades etc don't heal you like they normally would.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="no_healing" value="False" />
                    No Heals
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col border">
            <h3>Other Randomizations</h3>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="All normal enemies that spawn in the world are randomized.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="enemy_rando" value="False" />
                    Enemy Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Battle Crown platforms are randomized in their spawn location.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="battle_crown_rando" value="False" />
                    Battle Crown Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="The order of KRools boxing match will randomly order the sequence (Currently always ends on chunky).">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="k_rool_phase_order" value="True" checked/>
                    K Rool Phase Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="All prices in shops are randomized to a random number.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="shop_price_rando" value="False" />
                    Shop Price Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="The boss you can get in a level is different than normal.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="boss_location_rando" value="True" checked/>
                    Boss Location Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Bonus Barrels are randomly chosen from the pool of available Bonus Barrels.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="bonus_barrel_rando" value="True" checked/>
                    Bonus Barrel Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Loading Zones are randomly chosen from the pool of available Loading Zones.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="loading_zone_rando" value="True" checked/>
                    Loading Zone Rando
                </label>
            </div>
            <div class="form-check form-switch">
                <label title="Loading Zones will be coupled front to back.">
                    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="loading_zone_coupled" value="False" />
                    Loading Zone Coupling
                </label>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>